{"tid":828760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好憎同耶撚做同事","createTime":"2018-09-20T02:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T15:17:34.000Z","uid":193192,"like":93,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8581af6cc8f55b2f8e6ca65df2ac2d6f6b8b2803","tid":828760,"uid":193192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  無論遇到咩問題 都話一齊祈禱 希望上帝會指引<br />\n再唔係就話 呢D 問題係神既考驗<br />\n<br />\n大佬呀 與其你花時間係度9 up 不如快快手手解決問題啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到一班人一齊解決左佢既問題 佢就淨係識得講 感謝主 帶我地前行 指引我地道路 令我地成功解決到呢D 困難<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔通係神幫你做架咩? 係我地呀 ! 係咪應該多謝我地呀? <br />\n我地辛辛苦苦幫你解決既問題 功勞點解歸左俾上帝 <br />\n下次真係唔會再想幫你做野...<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔專重你既信仰 <br />\n但你開口埋口都係神既指引 都係上主既恩典<br />\n完全漠視其他人既功勞 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你下次有問題 自己祈禱等上帝打救啦 我唔會再幫"},{"pid":"79fabe239a983528cfd07381597f01f0b2c699d7","tid":828760,"uid":91931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a305a3b9c62dc1e0e5547a03f69e278df5121c24","tid":828760,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:25:20.000Z","msg":"感謝主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75cb9634535edf133c0090a5720fd00cde33e40f","tid":828760,"uid":200872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:26:21.000Z","msg":"主係全能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c642b76f012f66015f779404beb72fbb3a9bdcdc","tid":828760,"uid":56940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:26:51.000Z","msg":"有個耶撚負評左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f434307b2a7fb689192d4b5caea47c27e8b3f2","tid":828760,"uid":150515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8581af6cc8f55b2f8e6ca65df2ac2d6f6b8b2803","tid":828760,"uid":193192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  無論遇到咩問題 都話一齊祈禱 希望上帝會指引<br />\n再唔係就話 呢D 問題係神既考驗<br />\n<br />\n大佬呀 與其你花時間係度9 up 不如快快手手解決問題啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到一班人一齊解決左佢既問題 佢就淨係識得講 感謝主 帶我地前行 指引我地道路 令我地成功解決到呢D 困難<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔通係神幫你做架咩? 係我地呀 ! 係咪應該多謝我地呀? <br />\n我地辛辛苦苦幫你解決既問題 功勞點解歸左俾上帝 <br />\n下次真係唔會再想幫你做野...<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔專重你既信仰 <br />\n但你開口埋口都係神既指引 都係上主既恩典<br />\n完全漠視其他人既功勞 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你下次有問題 自己祈禱等上帝打救啦 我唔會再幫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:27:19.000Z","msg":"遲啲問你幾時一齊返教會   標準劇情啦"},{"pid":"3cabd5c73f60716bec1c623117e82b15c2716a14","tid":828760,"uid":71913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:29:46.000Z","msg":"有過耶撚同事 做野如果咁極端好大問題<br />\n<br />\n你老闆應該一早頂佢唔順<br />\n<br />\n我識個個最多食lunch前祈禱<br />\n<br />\n我理撚得佢 一野塞舊肉入口"},{"pid":"124d62c150bb1628e596a295d6fb23273f8139a2","tid":828760,"uid":193192,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有成班人係group 度搞下笑 吹下水既時候<br />\n永遠都要出嚟講下神 講下上帝 <br />\n有冇諗過人地唔想知? <br />\n你咁鍾意講 你返去你間教會講啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每次你一講完 成個group 靜晒呀!<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 係靜晒呀 !</span></span><br />\n你想人地點覆你 唔係話唔俾你講呀<br />\n但你都睇場合 睇話題呀<br />\n乜柒都要拉落神度做咩姐? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成group 人得你一個信神 你自己講飽佢啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇人應你都應該知咩事啦!!!"},{"pid":"ab652647b6fdecb2dcedb045983024b462f1eef3","tid":828760,"